<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Happy Roof"
  description="Happy Roof LLC Terms & Conditions. Website use, SMS consent, roofing service disclaimers, and governing law for Tampa Bay customers."
  canonical="https://happyroof.com/terms"
  ogTitle="Terms & Conditions | Happy Roof LLC"
  ogDescription="Happy Roof's Terms & Conditions covering website use, SMS consent, and service disclaimers."
  schema={schema}
>

<style is:inline>
.legal-body{background:#F5F5F5;color:#1a1a1a}
    .legal-body h2{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A;margin:2rem 0 .6rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #E0E0E0}
    .legal-body h2:first-of-type{border-top:none;padding-top:0;margin-top:0}
    .legal-body p{color:#888888;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:.9rem}
    .legal-body ul{color:#888888;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 .9rem 1.25rem;list-style:disc}
    .legal-body ul li{margin-bottom:.3rem}
    .legal-body a{color:#E6A817;text-decoration:underline}
    .legal-body a:hover{color:#2D8CC4}
    .highlight-box{background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;margin:1rem 0}
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<section style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:7rem 0 3rem;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
    <p style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#E6A817;margin-bottom:.75rem">Legal</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.8rem);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.88rem">Last updated: March 22, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Happy Roof LLC, Tampa Bay, FL</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTENT -->
<section class="legal-body">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-12">

    <p>Please read these Terms &amp; Conditions ("Terms") carefully before using the Happy Roof website (happyroof.com) or requesting services from <strong>Happy Roof LLC</strong> ("Happy Roof," "we," "us," or "our"). By accessing our website or submitting an inquiry, you agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>

    <h2>1. Services</h2>
    <p>Happy Roof LLC is a licensed roofing contractor serving the Tampa Bay, Florida area (State License #CCC1337380). Our services include residential and commercial roof replacement, repair, inspection, storm damage assessment, new construction roofing, and gutter services.</p>
    <p>Submitting a form or requesting an estimate does not constitute a contract for services. All work is governed by a separate written agreement signed by both parties prior to commencement.</p>

    <h2>2. Website Use</h2>
    <p>You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not infringe the rights of others. You may not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the site to transmit unsolicited or unauthorized advertising</li>
      <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any portion of the website</li>
      <li>Use automated tools to scrape, crawl, or harvest data from the site</li>
      <li>Misrepresent your identity or affiliation when contacting us</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. SMS &amp; Communications Consent</h2>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p><strong>By submitting a form on this website with the SMS consent box checked, you expressly consent to receive text messages from Happy Roof LLC</strong> at the mobile number you provide.</p>
      <p><strong>Types of messages you will receive:</strong> You may receive account alerts, updates, and promotional messages.</p>
      <p><strong>Message frequency varies</strong> based on your inquiry and project status. Message and data rates may apply.</p>
      <p>To opt out at any time, reply <strong>STOP</strong> or <strong>CANCEL</strong> to any message. For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> or contact us at <a href="mailto:info@happyroof.com">info@happyroof.com</a> or call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number">(813) 595-7663</a>.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0"><strong>Consent to receive SMS messages is not a condition of purchasing any services.</strong> You may uncheck the SMS consent box on any form to withhold consent.</p>
    </div>
    <p>For full details on our messaging practices, see our <a href="https://www.happyroof.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>4. Estimates &amp; Quotes</h2>
    <p>Any estimate or quote provided, whether online, by phone, or in person, is a good-faith approximation based on available information. Final pricing may vary based on actual site conditions, material availability, scope changes, or unforeseen circumstances discovered during work. All final pricing will be confirmed in a written contract before work begins.</p>

    <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All content on this website, including text, images, logos, graphics, and the Happy Roof name and smiley face mark, is the property of Happy Roof LLC and protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our prior written consent.</p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our website may link to or integrate third-party services, including Enhancify for financing. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of third-party websites. Use of third-party services is subject to their respective terms and privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>This website and its content are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. Happy Roof LLC does not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components. We make no warranties regarding the accuracy or completeness of any information on this site.</p>
    <p><em>Note: Warranties on actual roofing work are governed by your individual service contract and applicable manufacturer warranties, not by these website Terms.</em></p>

    <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Happy Roof LLC shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of this website or reliance on any information provided herein. Our total liability for any claim related to this website shall not exceed $100.</p>
    <p>Nothing in these Terms limits our liability for fraud, gross negligence, or any liability that cannot be excluded under Florida law.</p>

    <h2>9. Indemnification</h2>
    <p>You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Happy Roof LLC and its officers, employees, and agents from any claims, liabilities, damages, and expenses (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising from your violation of these Terms or misuse of this website.</p>

    <h2>10. Privacy</h2>
    <p>Your use of this website is also governed by our <a href="https://www.happyroof.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.</p>

    <h2>11. Governing Law &amp; Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes arising under these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the state and federal courts located in Hillsborough County, Florida.</p>
    <p>Before initiating any formal legal proceeding, you agree to contact us in good faith at <a href="mailto:info@happyroof.com">info@happyroof.com</a> to attempt to resolve the dispute informally.</p>

    <h2>12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes take effect when posted to this page. Continued use of our website after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms. We will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page when changes are made.</p>

