      <p style="margin-bottom:.3rem">Tampa Bay, FL &nbsp;·&nbsp; License #CCC1337380</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:.3rem">Email: <a href="mailto:info@happyroof.com">info@happyroof.com</a></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0">Phone: <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number">(813) 595-7663</a></p>
